           <a class="jiathis_counter_style"></a> 
          </div> 
          <br />
          <br /> 
          <script type="text/javascript" src="http://v2.jiathis.com/code/jia.js" charset="utf-8"></script> 
          <!-- JiaThis Button END -->
         </div>
         <div style="clear:both; margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px;"></div>
         <p><a href="http://www.pcdigest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/1_2008040422035415.jpg"></a><a href="http://www.pcdigest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/1_2008040422035415.jpg"></a><a href="http://www.pcdigest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/1_200804042203547.jpg"><img class="alignleft alignnone size-medium wp-image-698" style="float: left;" title="1_200804042203547" src="http://www.pcdigest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/1_200804042203547-300x205.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="205" /></a></p> 
         <p>&nbsp;</p> 
         <p>&nbsp;</p> 
         <p>&nbsp;</p> 
         <p>系统全部更新完毕之后是这么一个界面，中间的两个就是增加的录音和录像功能的快捷方式。总体说来还是不错的，另外，这个桌面也还是很好看的。说到这里就得赞一下这个版本的桌面图片了，有好几张我都很喜欢，最喜欢的那张白色的图片！&nbsp;</p> 
         <p>&nbsp;</p> 
         <p><span id="more-696"></span></p> 
         <p><a href="http://www.pcdigest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/1_2008040422035415.jpg"><img class="alignleft alignnone size-medium wp-image-697" style="float: left;" title="1_2008040422035415" src="http://www.pcdigest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/1_2008040422035415-300x210.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="210" /></a>这几张背景都是非常好看的，其中，右上那张和正中间白色的这张素雅而神秘，我最喜欢，一张一张轮流用吧！这个月先用绿色那个界面。</p> 
         <p><a href="http://www.pcdigest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/1_2008040422035415.jpg"></a><a href="http://www.pcdigest.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/1_2008040422035415.jpg"></a></p> 
         <p>
          <!--more--></p> 
        </div>
